an><hr size=1> Ok, I've heard 2 theories on exp with pets:<br>
<br>
A) If you do more damage then your pet (which is <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> very</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> easy with the 34 pet), you get all the exp.<br>
<br>
2) If you have a pet, no matter how much damage you both do, you still split the exp.<br>
<br>
Which is correct??<br>
